                        | Your Pledge Means A Lot To Us
            //label.cssPageHeaderTitleText Thank You For Your Considering A Pledge To Collider-X
        .cssDonationPanels
            .fiatDonationPanel.cssFiatDonatePanel
                form.fiat-donation-form(action='/charge', method='post')
                    .cssDonateVisibleElements
                        label.paymentAmount-label  You just donated #{amount} in #{currency} to the Blockchain research and development hub. As a sponsor, we will ensure that you enjoy all of the perks and benefits of our Blockchain R&D hub and that our research efforts will reflect your contributions.